premise_source_doc_sentence: Propelled to international success by social media , One Direction 's five albums , Up All Night  (  2011  )  , Take Me Home  (  2012  )  , Midnight Memories  (  2013  )  , Four  (  2014  )  , and Made in the A.M.  (  2015  )  , topped charts in most major markets , and generated hit singles including `` What Makes You Beautiful '' , `` Live While We 're Young '' , `` Best Song Ever '' , `` Story of My Life '' , and `` Drag Me Down '' .
